"The encyclopedia of molecular biology"

"The Encyclopedia houses two types of article entry. Short articles of up to 100 words offer a short definition which is fully cross-referenced to article length entries of between 1,000 - 3,000 words. This unique cross-reference system allows the reader to approach their subject at the required level of detail and sophistication"
" Sinh học phân tử, Bách khoa toàn thư"
